5: What's with all the materials here?
9:
Why, we're building a house on the
beach, of course!
13:
To us it may just be a pile of lumber,
but to those boys it represents the
realization of a BEAUTIFUL dream!
Would you be so kind as to help out?
16:
I would of course be willing to help
out, but I think we could use more
information—what's this about a
dream, exactly?
19:
I know right! We were totally
surprised too, bros. It's like, I had a
dream within me all along, but I
didn't realize it, you know?
21:
Our bro was talking with Marguerite
over some drinks, and he had a
breakthrough. He was like, "What if
we started a business?", and we
were like, "Bro!"
23:
So we went and got all this lumber
and stuff here to start building our
own restaurant!
26:
Ah, there is nothing more RADIANT
than helping someone realize their
dream! A good deed breeds
another—a cycle of constant BEAUTY!
30:
I've already spoken to the managers
of this island—we're safe to start
building! Let's build a place where
you can truly SHINE, boys.
36:
Wow, it really looks like a proper
restaurant!
39:
A restaurant with an excellent view
of the sea—this could actually turn
out well for them.
42:
Indeed, especially given the
BEAUTIFUL interior! It was designed
according to my tastes, yes, but I'm
sure you'll agree it's done with
subtlety!
45:
That's all thanks to John—he did all
the decorating!
48:
Yeah, bro, you did such a sweet job.
Our restaurant is gonna be on fleek!
50:
Thanks, bro, I'm flattered! But yeah,
this was all thanks to Marguerite's
awesome instructions!
52:
We need some sick outfits to go with
this decor—I sketched up a few
designs already, actually...
57:
Well, I'm thinking of something that
looks like this...
61:
SPLENDID! Swashbuckling, yet
pristine! A perfect fusion for a
seaside restaurant!
64:
You truly have an eye for fashion,
Gary.
67:
Th-thank you! I'll make matching
outfits for everyone too!
70:
Everyone seems real motivated. Still,
you've got a ways to go before
you're ready to open, don't you?
75:
Heh, of course! We've still got the
most important thing to take care
of—the FOOD! We need to serve the
most beautiful dishes possible!
78:
Bro, are we gonna hire some pro
chefs?
80:
But it's like, our restaurant, so maybe
WE should cook the food, bro?
82:
I dunno, bros, I don't think we're THAT
good at cooking...
85:
Where there's a will, there's a way!
It's more than possible to learn how
to cook. Isn't that right, Alk?
88:
My beautiful Alk, with that lovely
face that lights up every time you
help another! Would you grace us
with another one of your smiles?
92:
Haha, okay, you don't need to be so
extra. I guess I could teach the guys
how to make a few simple dishes
real quick!
97:
That's it! That's the face! The
smile!
So STUNNING!
101:
Scott, my dear. What do you think
we should do?
108:
Bros, what were we thinking? We
can't do this... Running a restaurant
isn't a game. We have to do like,
actual business stuff...
110:
Besides, who would even want to
come to a restaurant run by some
rich kid and his bros? They'll never
take us seriously... And also...
111:
I'm not talented like you bros, all
right?!
114:
A thoroughly unmanageable lad,
that one.
117: Well then. John, Gary, come along.
121:
I wonder what he would benefit
most from now... Should I scold him
or console him?
125:
No, perhaps neither is the answer.
There is something more BEAUTIFUL
that lies in wait here.
130:
Forget the haters! Who cares if they
don't believe in us? We believe in
EACH OTHER, bro.
134:
You're not like the others, you say? I
disagree. All three of you share
something important in common:
138:
You are MARVELOUS! Bloom, my
friends! Aspire to the heights of
BEAUTY, be true to yourselves, and
never forsake the path you know to
be right!
